embeds.title: Status Key
embeds.description:
---------------------
🟢  - Working
🟡 - Under Development
🟠 - Updating
🔴 - Not Working
🔵 - Unknown
---------------------

fields.name: 🟢  - Working
fields.value: The app is working functionally with no to minimal errors.

fields.name: 🟡 - Under Development
fields.value: The app is currently under development and is not yet released. It should be available soon.

fields.name: 🟠 - Updating
fields.value: The app is currently updating and a stable release should be sent in downloads soon.

fields.name: 🔴 - Not Working
fields.value: The app is currently broken, not working, detected, or deleted (possibly due to legal action). More information should be displayed in downloads.

fields.name: 🔵 - Unknown
fields.value: The app is currently in an unknown state, usually due to limitations, or if the bot goes offline.

footer.text: Any questions, please make a ticket.
